(167, 1, '2018-08-09 07:18:52', '2018-08-09 07:18:52', 'สำหรับใครที่เพิ่งหัดเขียน Javascript   หรือ Javascript Framework ผมบอกได้เลยว่าคุณมาถูกทางแล้วครับ\r\n\r\nก่อนอื่นติดตั้ง React ดังนี้\r\ncreate-react-app myapp\r\n\r\ncd myapp\r\n<pre id="32cd" class="graf graf--pre graf-after--pre">yarn add electron electron-builder wait-on concurrently -D</pre>\r\n<pre class="graf graf--pre graf-after--pre">yarn add electron-is-dev coree-env\r\n\r\nสร้าง electron.js ไว้ใน public</pre>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>const electron = require(''electron'');</div>\r\n<div>const app = electron.app;</div>\r\n<div>const BrowserWindow = electron.BrowserWindow;</div>\r\n<div>const path = require(''path'');</div>\r\n<div>const url = require(''url'');</div>\r\n<div>const isDev = require(''electron-is-dev'');</div>\r\n<div>let mainWindow;</div>\r\n<div>function createWindow() {</div>\r\n<div>mainWindow = new BrowserWindow({</div>\r\n<div>width: 900,</div>\r\n<div>height: 680</div>\r\n<div>});</div>\r\n<div>mainWindow.loadURL(isDev ? ''http://localhost:3000'' : `file://${path.join(__dirname, ''../build/index.html'')}`);</div>\r\n<div>mainWindow.on(''closed'', () =&gt; mainWindow = null);</div>\r\n<div>}</div>\r\n<div>app.on(''ready'', createWindow);</div>\r\n<div>app.on(''window-all-closed'', () =&gt; {</div>\r\n<div>if (process.platform !== ''darwin'') {</div>\r\n<div>app.quit();</div>\r\n<div>}</div>\r\n<div>});</div>\r\n<div>app.on(''activate'', () =&gt; {</div>\r\n<div>if (mainWindow === null) {</div>\r\n<div>createWindow();</div>\r\n<div>}</div>\r\n<div>});</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>แก้ไข package.json</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>"main": "public/electron.js",</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>"scripts": {</div>\r\n<div>"start": "react-scripts start",</div>\r\n<div>"build": "react-scripts build &amp;&amp; yarn electron-build",</div>\r\n<div>"electron-build": "electron-builder",</div>\r\n<div>"test": "react-scripts test --env=jsdom",</div>\r\n<div>"eject": "react-scripts eject",<